    <item>
      <title>Eskom 考虑私人和外国选择 210 亿美元的电网建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/eskom-mulls-private-foreign-options-on-21-billion-grid-build</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国有电力公司 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 表示，随着更多可再生能源发电并网，该公司正在与政府部门就私人和外国选项进行谈判，以资助 ​​3900 亿兰特（210 亿美元）扩建其输电网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/eskom-mulls-private-foreign-options-on-21-billion-grid-build</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:25:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特里谢：公共债务水平看起来比雷曼危机之前更令人担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/trichet-public-debt-is-more-worrying-than-before-lehman-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前行长让-克洛德·特里谢 (Jean-Claude Trichet) 讨论了公共债务以及他为何认为股市存在潜在调整的风险。特里谢在接受彭博电视台采访时表示：“当我查看一些指标时，例如发达经济体的总体未偿公共债务，我看到雷曼兄弟之前的国内生产总值的75%。今天我看到的是114%。” （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/trichet-public-debt-is-more-worrying-than-before-lehman-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着重组困境加深，电池制造商瓦尔塔股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/battery-maker-varta-plunges-as-restructuring-woes-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国电池制造商瓦尔塔股份公司(Varta AG)表示，各业务领域的进一步恶化意味着去年与银行达成的重组计划不再合适，该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/battery-maker-varta-plunges-as-restructuring-woes-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜价继续上涨，飙升至 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价继续上涨，触及 22 个月来的最高水平，因为投资者押注减少的矿产供应将难以跟上全球需求的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国出口降幅超预期复苏受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chinese-exports-drop-in-blow-to-hopes-for-economic-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份中国出口大幅下滑，对海外销售的蓬勃发展将抵消国内需求疲软并推动世界第二大经济体增长的希望造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chinese-exports-drop-in-blow-to-hopes-for-economic-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:17:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国限制航班频率，中国航空公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-airlines-slump-on-us-moves-to-limit-flight-frequencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对美国航空公司试图阻止世界最大两个经济体之间增加航班频率的消息做出反应，中国最大航空公司的股价周五暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-airlines-slump-on-us-moves-to-limit-flight-frequencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:01:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联金融集团称将讨论购买 HDFC 部门 17 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/mufg-said-to-discuss-buying-1-7-billion-stake-in-hdfc-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，三菱日联金融集团 (Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group Inc.) 正在洽谈收购 HDFC Bank Ltd. 消费贷款部门约 17 亿美元的股份，以满足印度不断增长的个人融资贷款需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/mufg-said-to-discuss-buying-1-7-billion-stake-in-hdfc-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯托纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行是时候与美联储分道扬镳了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/it-s-time-for-the-ecb-to-diverge-from-the-fed-stournaras-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员雅尼斯·斯图尔纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行不应该害怕改变其“过于谨慎”的利率立场，偏离美联储的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/it-s-time-for-the-ecb-to-diverge-from-the-fed-stournaras-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
